msgstr ""
"Justerar spelets svårighet till <guimenuitem>Lätt</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Normal</guimenuitem> eller <guimenuitem>Svår</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &kapman; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</guimenu> and "
